Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:18.40,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:29.86,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.79,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:47.92,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:56.85,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:08.74,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.63,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:26.47,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:36.27,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:29.86,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.79,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:47.92,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:56.85,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:08.74,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.63,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:26.47,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:36.27,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:47.20,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(230,80)}Ep. 35 - Showdown
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:55.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What? They're detonating it so close to here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:55.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:01:59.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:04.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a landslide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:05.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:09.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get out of there, everyone!\NThere's a landslide!
Comment: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:11.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.05,0:02:14.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone escape!\NA wall of rock is coming your way! 
Comment: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:15.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:20.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:46.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A word came out that a major landslide occurred\Nat the Mount Lofty quarry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:50.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's where our dad was working.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:03.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, you should calm down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I am calm enough as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:10.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be pacing back and forth\Nif that was so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:15.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I just can't help\Nroaming through the room without realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure dad is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:23.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When John returns with more news,\Nwe'll know for sure where dad is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:30.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear Lord, I just beg you\Nto keep that man safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:40.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little also can't stop pacing through the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:43.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, he'd be sleeping in his doghouse by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He must also be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:47.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:53.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone in the house\Nis restless because of dad, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:55.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So you think Little can feel that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:56.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget how smart Little is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I hope dad is alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:02.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:05.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even fathom\Nsomething bad happening to dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:07.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So he's safe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:09.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. {\i1}Must{\i0} be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:12.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you sleepy, Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay awake for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:17.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you have a school tomorrow,\Nso better go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like sleeping at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:24.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little dashed towards the street!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Little, what is it?
Comment: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:39.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:46.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You're also worried about Mr. Popple?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:57.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So, you couldn't find out if dad is alright or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:05:01.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. They had to evacuate\Nfive or six men with the most serious injuries. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But thankfully, Mr. Popple wasn't among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:08.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, there were seemingly multiple people\Nwith light injuries still on the site.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:13.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't determine\Nexactly how severe their injuries were. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:15.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And why didn't they evacuate the rest of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:18.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like they can do any quarrying this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:22.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, they only have three carriages there,\Nso they can't evacuate everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:26.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I want to find a carriage\Nand go to the quarry myself right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:28.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to know if dad is alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:29.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:29.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment, you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:35.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The road to the quarry is narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:41.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There wouldn't be enough space for carriages heading there and returning carriages to pass by each other. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:43.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The road is still closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:46.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, probably. But I think\Nthey'll let you pass in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:54.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'm going to the quarry\Nfirst thing in the morning tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:58.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At a time like this, I can't wait even a second more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:00.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but do you have a carriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a wagon or an oxcart?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:04.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, we'll have to borrow one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:04.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whom from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:09.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Who could lend their cart to us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:14.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The closest one is Mr. Pettywell's.\NMoreover, he has a fleet-footed carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:16.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say Mr. Pettywell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Pettywell...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:24.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At a time like this, should it come from Mr. Pettywell or whoever else, I wouldn't look down on any carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But him, of all people...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:29.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you've got anyone else on your mind,\Nwilling to lend it to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Parker has a cart as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But that man is living at the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:38.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Ben could borrow\None of the carriage from the port customs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:41.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You silly, Ben is also at the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:44.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So we've no choice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:47.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll go try\Nto implore with Mr. Pettywell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But will he really be willing to lend it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:52.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If I explain our circumstances,\NI'm sure he'll be cooperative. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:57.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, would you please go with mom\Nto the quarry tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:04.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That was rude of you.\NJohn has work tomorrow, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but isn't it your day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:06.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:10.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've driven a horse-drawn carriage\Nmany times before. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:11.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,John, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with your mother.
Comment: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:16.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I still feel bad, doing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:22.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't. It's like I'm almost a member\Nof the Popple family already anyway. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:27.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, Mr. Popple's... No, father's condition\Nconcerns me just as much as everyone else. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:29.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And you two should long be in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:35.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:40.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I'll skip the school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:41.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:44.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm that much worried about dad,\NI can't do any studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:47.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:50.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me to take care about father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:53.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, better put your mind\Nto studying as hard as you can. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:08:00.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, go to bed now.\NYou're going to school as usual. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to school, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:29.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here, okay?\NI'll try to return as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:44.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Little.\NLucy went to school, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:49.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning. Glad to see you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:54.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How did it go?\NDid Mr. Pettywell let you borrow his cart?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:55.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We were just about to go there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'm coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't bite, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:22.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We should be fine if we stand still.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:24.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If we stand still.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:29.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But man, for how long will he keep us waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Really, that's very rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:45.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:51.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for the inconvenience, but Master is still resting, therefore he cannot receive you right now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:55.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We could come a little later, if so. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:58.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... No, that really wouldn't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:09:59.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:02.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well... You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:07.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite possible that Master\Nwould still be resting even then, therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:11.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you explained\Nexhaustively to Mr. Pettywell
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:15.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,why Mrs. Popple desperately needs\Nthat carriage right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:21.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I mean, no.\NAs I said, Master is still sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:23.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so that's what it's all about? 
Comment: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:24.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:27.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We get it. You don't want to lie to us. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:29.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, let's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Comment: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:32.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:36.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Can't you do something about that dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:38.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No. It doesn't listen to me either. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:39.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He looks inclined to bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:41.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Silver! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:44.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Move out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:50.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, please go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're one troublesome guy. 
Comment: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:09.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:11.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that Mr. Pettywell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:15.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now, mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:17.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a cart we could lend somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But where could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:21.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try asking from everyone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I'm coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:28.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did dad die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:32.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you possibly ask if he is dead or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:38.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because nobody wants to tell me openly... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:40.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:44.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You see, there's been an accident\Non a quarry where dad works.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:50.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And so, everyone's worried\Nabout whether or not dad had been injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:51.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So he's injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:54.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No. We can't know for sure yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:58.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why mom prepares to go to the quarry herself\Nto check on dad's health.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:02.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, dad is well, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:06.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't properly understand\Neven one bit of it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:16.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How did it go? Did you manage\Nto borrow a carriage, mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:21.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When we came to ask for it,\NMr. Pettywell's servant told us he is still sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:24.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:26.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But then, where are Clara and John?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:31.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if we'd come to Mr. Bernard's office,\Nhe could give us some advise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:35.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A well-connected man such as him\Nwould definitely know someone.  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:39.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But... What if he went out\Non a surveying mission in the hinterland again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:42.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he's in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:51.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And now, does anyone here\Nhave an answer to this question?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:53.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:56.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:12:58.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Answer the question I just asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:07.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Lucy-May Popple?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:08.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:13.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What was the question you just asked -\NI don't know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:15.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So you weren't listening again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:15.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Stand by the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:19.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:28.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that clear? Everyone else\Nneeds to stay concentrated, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:31.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,During the class, you always listen carefully\Nto what teacher says.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:37.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Looking to the sides, or thinking about other things,\Nas well as talking to the others is unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:38.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:39.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, you understand too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:41.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, answer this new question, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:45.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:54.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm... So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:14:00.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I digressed to tell you off\Nand forgot what it was about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:04.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, everyone, what was I\Nasking you just a moment ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:15.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone else we could ask? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:17.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I know of... 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:21.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If only Mr. Bernard was here,\Nhe'd think of something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:23.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, let's be on our way. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:39.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:42.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not happening. They need it for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:42.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:45.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I know of one more person with an oxcart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head there at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. It's a little far, though. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't suppose\Nthey'll let us borrow that carriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:04.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom is probably beside herself back at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:05.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find where to borrow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:08.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Let's hurry up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Clara!
Comment: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Someone called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:21.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:22.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:24.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Here! I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:29.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:32.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, leg hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:38.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Just a bit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You know I was worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:45.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really? Seemed to me like you\Ndidn't even understand what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:47.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Tob.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, I'm going to the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Make sure to apologize to Mrs. Mac!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:16:00.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll have my leave too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:04.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, John. I'm really sorry\Nfor all the trouble you had to go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:09.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's more important, Mr. Popple, don't you think\Nyou should see a doctor about your leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:12.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What for? It's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:15.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I just twisted my ankle\Nwhile helping to carry the wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:16.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it hurts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:18.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I sit like that, it's perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,John, you want to go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Well, Mr. Popple, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:25.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:26.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:34.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,John is exaggerating.\NIt's really nothing more than a twisted ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:35.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:38.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,See? Maybe the bone is fractured, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:42.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was naturally shocked when you\Nentered this room limping so much. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense! It'll heal in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:48.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not supposed to worry\Nsince it's not even my leg, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:52.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, dad, you won't go to work\Nat the quarry ever again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:56.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I will go. But that quarry\Nwill be shut down for some while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:58.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They're afraid there'd be another landslide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:01.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to go to the quarry anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:04.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well if there was any other good job for me,\NI wouldn't be going to the quarry. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:08.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I guess no other job\Nfits you quite like farming. Right, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:11.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, I'll go get a bit of sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:14.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep a wink last night,\Nhaving to look after the injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:16.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. It's best that you go to sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:17.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:20.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:21.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's mighty strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:31.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:34.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Were you behaving well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:55.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, did I make you worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:59.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How could you tell it's me with your eyes closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:04.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy to tell. Although the school\Nended pretty early today, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher wasn't feeling too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:07.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:10.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What about your leg?\NI was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:12.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Hurts a little, but that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:18.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take Kate along\Nand we'll go fetch Dr. Deighton for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:30.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it's just a leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:33.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, he wasn't in the way of falling stones,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:38.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,but hurt his leg later, while helping transport\Nthe wounded, which strikes me as careless, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:40.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can't say it's the same for me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:44.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, it's proof dad was working\Nlike mad for people he barely knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:46.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Little? Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:00.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We can't rest now! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:05.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:06.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:07.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You think there's a fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:08.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:12.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And it's coming exactly\Nfrom where Doctor Deighton lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:16.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Deighton lives in a brick house,\Nwhich can't catch fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:19.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But our former house is made of wood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You think it's that cabin that's burning?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Let go or you'll regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:33.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop resisting, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:38.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already, let him go now.\NThis Doctor can't hope to put out that fire on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:40.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's also true. There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:42.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:47.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:49.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, what has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:53.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,These bandits set fire to the shack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So it's an arson?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:05.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Young ladies, do we look like arsonists to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:06.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But Doctor said...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:12.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The owner of this building gave us\Nan explicit order to burn the shack down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:14.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This is not the same as arson! No, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:16.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The owner of this building...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's Pettywell, Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:21.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next, they'll put fire to my house as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:25.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, Doctor. That house\Nwould be a pain to set ablaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:29.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,For that house, we'll bring a huge hammer\Nto tear it down nice and easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:32.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So you already have plans\Nto come for my house too? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:36.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Those were the direct orders\Nwe've received from Mr. Pettywell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:40.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it'd be better if you moved out\Nof that house by then, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:48.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This house was built with blood and sweat\Nof those girls' father and brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:50.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And it's the best one I've ever lived in! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:53.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad the land now belongs to Mr. Pettywell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But the building is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:58.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The shack is collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:11.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What the... What are you saying, Lucy-May?
Comment: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:11.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:12.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:19.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This house holds countless memories from the first two years we spent in it after coming to Southern Australia! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:22.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So it's heartbreaking\Nto see it turned into ashes like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:27.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, you seem to enjoy it,\Nsaying "how beautiful!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:28.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:34.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what brings you two here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:37.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Doctor, we need you to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:39.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father injured his leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:43.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Really? That's a no-go?\NSo, is the injury very bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:48.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But the pain is evidently so bad,\Neven our enduring dad agreed to us fetching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.53,0:21:50.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll go there right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:51.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just let me grab my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:21:58.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.82,0:22:02.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's Mr. Pettywell's carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:04.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't want to see him now! 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:07.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's tell him all we think\Nabout him letting the house ablaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:21.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All right'o...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:24.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, good job, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.59,0:22:26.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.12,0:22:29.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it burns really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:31.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong, Silver?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:40.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, if it isn't daughters of that Popple?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:43.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You went to the trouble\Nof coming here to watch the house burn?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.45,0:22:50.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that doesn't seem right. You weren't\Nsupposed to know I'm going to burn this shack.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:51.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Silver!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:54.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If need be, feel free to bite him to death, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.19,0:23:00.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, you're not gonna tell Little to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:07.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that bulldog too... 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.21,0:23:09.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You have to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.02,0:23:16.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:18.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're in for quite a show! 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:22.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:27.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Pettywell, a man like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:43.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To be perfectly frank, back then,\Neven I myself wanted to order him to do just that - 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:48.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,tear that bulldog to shreds there and then! 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.40,0:24:00.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Back off, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.34,0:24:07.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Inside a bird nest I spotted by chance,\NI found some money!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.73,0:24:10.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Though it was just five shillings,\Nthey came in really handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.60,0:24:14.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Lucy-May of the Southern Rainbow:\N"Five Shillings in the Nest".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:16.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
